setTimeout.name: setTimeout
setTimeout.signature: function setTimeout(functionRef: (...args: any[]) => void, delay: number, ...args: any[]): TimeoutID;
setTimeout.documentation:
This module provides setInterval, setTimeout and co.
Set a timer that executes a function once the timer expires.

clearTimeout.name: clearTimeout
clearTimeout.documentation: Cancels a timer previously set with setTimeout().

setInterval.name: setInterval
setInterval.signature: function setInterval(functionRef: (...args: any[]) => void, delay: number, ...args: any[]): IntervalID;
setInterval.documentation: Repeatedly execute a function, with a fixed time delay between each call.

clearInterval.name: clearInterval
clearInterval.documentation: Cancels an interval previously set with setInterval().

TimeoutID.name: TimeoutID
TimeoutID.documentation: Type alias for a timer id.

IntervalID.name: IntervalID
IntervalID.documentation: Type alias for a interval id.
